- **Project:** Slidev presentation.
- **Runtime/PM:** Use `bun` exclusively (`bun install`, `bun run ...`).
- **Main File:** `./slides.md`.
- **New Slides:** Create in `./pages/`, import via `## src: ./pages/[filename].md`.
- **Theme:** Use `@slidev/theme-default`. Do not create custom themes.
- **Styling:** Use UnoCSS, scoped `<style>`, or global styles (`./style.css` / `./styles/index.ts`). See `./docs/how-to-styling.md`.
- **Assets:** Store in `./public/`.
- **Commands:** `bun run dev` (start), `bun run build`, `bun run export`.
- **Docs:** Start with `./docs/how-to-overview.md`.
- **Git:** Do not perform any Git operations.